Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:02.67,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:05.63,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}High school student Shin'ichi was forced to take a pill that shrunk him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:07.24,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My mind is still that of a great detective, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:09.00,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Using my keen powers of deduction,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.67,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I solve every kind of case there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:12.27,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's case takes place during a spring festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:13.74,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Even if it's hidden behind the lens of a camera,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:15.64,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}there is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:56.61,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We now go live to Saitama Prefecture's\NTenkaichi Night Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:59.15,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The Tenkaichi Night Festival is famous for the bonfires
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:02.25,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}that spell out the word "Tenkaichi" on three separate mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:05.09,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The lighting of the letters is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:08.42,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Can't you look for it more quietly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:11.26,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. Just when I thought you went to the festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:13.69,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,you're already back here lookin' for your wallet or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.30,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can't even take a nice, relaxin' bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:19.40,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't forgotten about your promise for tonight, have you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:20.20,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:25.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! I came along because you said you'd celebrate with me—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:27.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that get-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:30.81,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And what happened in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:33.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but tonight's plans are cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:39.22,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the person we would be honoring tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:42.79,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Saitama prefecture's Tenkaichi Night Festival is now underway!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:46.49,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Look! The character for "Ten" has just been lit up on the mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:49.02,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:56.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing personal, Imatake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:03.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it sounded like there was a gunshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:05.33,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:35.67,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The last character, "Ichi", is lit up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:43.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At this festival, the characters for "Tenkaichi"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:48.52,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,are lit up on three mountains in the hopes of a good harvest this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:54.43,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Almost entirely a copy of Kyoto's Daimonji festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:58.96,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Staying at an inn and going to a festival sure is nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:02.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is! Don't you agree, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:04.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:06.13,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If I didn't have that, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:10.14,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I hate having her treat me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.02,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take a picture for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:21.69,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.79,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:26.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take it with that "Ichi" character behind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.96,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ready? Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.30,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:36.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A balloon got into the shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:42.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm writing about the various festivals in this region.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:46.11,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's what these pictures are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:47.88,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're a writer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:51.95,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're so{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} tan{\r} that I thought you might play sports or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:56.82,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got this from work. I often go overseas, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:01.62,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Norikazu Sasai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:12.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I used to write novels under\Nthe penname of Tomokazu Imai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:14.81,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:17.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I read a lot of his stuff in junior high!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:19.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:24.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that Satoru Imatake used that name for his debut...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:26.35,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Imatake and I are old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:28.72,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We used to write things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:31.49,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With the Satoru Imatake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:33.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We both came here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.16,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thought we'd drink the night away
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:38.96,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,in celebration of his winning the Naomoto Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:41.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:44.17,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Take off your jacket if you're hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:47.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This would make a good picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:49.11,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take a couple more shots for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:50.44,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:06:00.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Norikazu Sasai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:01.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:04.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Detective Yokomizo from the Saitama Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:08.53,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to ask you about Satoru Imatake{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:10.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Has something happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's been murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:16.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In the hotel room you were both staying in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:20.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The murder weapon was a pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:23.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The murder took place just 2 or 3 minutes after 8 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:25.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer was a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:28.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He fled the room immediately afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:30.52,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're completely sure about all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:36.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The TV coverage of the festival had just started...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.46,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shot cleanly through the head...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:45.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:50.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, aren't you the famous detective Kogoro Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:53.87,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that would be me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:07:00.51,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I read about those difficult cases that you solve all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:02.48,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.82,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I was the one who solved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.99,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please look around as you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:10.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be honored if you assisted me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:24.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:27.54,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:29.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Toothpaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:39.39,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A toothbrush! Was the victim killed while brushing his teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:41.65,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're always getting in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:44.19,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Detective Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.36,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This smells greatly of a robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.35,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:55.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Only the money has been removed from the victim's wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:58.64,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Plus the perpetrator ransacked the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:02.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This was an ordinary crime done for monetary gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:07.11,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the fact that the victim fell near the front door,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:09.92,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,most likely someone had knocked on the door
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:13.11,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and shot him the instant he opened it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:16.36,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But Detective Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:19.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The robbery was just a disguise;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.92,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,the real killer was the room's other occupant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:26.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, you can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.70,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The murder took place around 8, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:31.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, I have an alibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:35.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was at the Tenkaichi Night Festival when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:38.44,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's where I met Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:39.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.31,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:44.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I believe it was during the last half of the festival that we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:47.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! I was there from the very start!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:50.22,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you think I'm lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:51.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...then have this developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.59,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It should prove that my alibi is real!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:57.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,OK! Get this developed right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.09,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:03.00,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Detective Yokomizo is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:05.31,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This was no robbery!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:08.17,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The victim and the killer knew each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:11.21,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's almost certainly him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:14.25,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But what's with that big smile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:17.68,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Just what sort of alibi does\Nhe have in that camera?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:22.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Seven pictures in all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:26.59,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But what do these have to do with his alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.26,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I took this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:33.27,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See! It has Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s balloon in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:37.87,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We met Sasai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nwhen the "Ichi" character was lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:42.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it's past 8:40 when "Ichi" is lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:44.68,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The murder took place at 8:02 or 8:03.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:47.65,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think you could make it to the festival grounds in 40 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.31,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,if you rushed by car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Yokomizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:55.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After the first character, "Ten", is lit at 8:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:58.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,about how long does it continue to burn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:01.53,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Usually until about 8:25 or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:03.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have a look at this picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:12.57,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This proves that he was at the festival grounds before 8:25, at the latest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:14.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The murder was at 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.31,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how fast you drive,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:20.77,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,it's impossible to go from here to the festival grounds in 25 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:25.45,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations. Your alibi is airtight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:30.02,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How can this be? How can that picture be there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:35.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is photographic alteration out of the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.63,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Multiple exposures or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:39.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Someone good with cameras could easily—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:42.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. I handed the camera directly over to you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.74,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and asked you to develop the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:47.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, it was a disposable camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:50.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I could have done no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:53.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who developed the film, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:53.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:57.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There were no signs of the camera or film being tampered with!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:58.72,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Detective Yokomizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:04.82,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You already knew he was at the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:08.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I heard from the hotel's front desk\Nthat Sasai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left around 7:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:15.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They remembered because he was constantly asking the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:20.11,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was because I wanted to make it in time for the "Ten" character.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:23.88,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, I forgot my watch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:27.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something bugs me about everything you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost as if you were trying to make an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:31.82,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:34.79,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I would appreciate it if you would stop wasting time like this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and get to the real task at hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:41.19,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,like finding out who killed my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.30,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Imatake{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.40,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.27,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.87,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Imatake{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:54.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,he was taken down to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:55.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who might you be, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:59.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Yamada, from the monthly magazine {\i1}Literature Era{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:04.72,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I rushed here as soon as the police called me, but I guess he really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:08.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Literature Era{\i0}? Didn't Imatake{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:10.72,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it published his "Heroic Sword Legend" series.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:13.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you Sasai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:14.49,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:17.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Imatake did mention that his deadline was coming up soon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but he still wasn't done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:23.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! His deadline was tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:24.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.31,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I ask someone else to write something, there isn't enough time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:31.24,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and nothing would ever be as good as his!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:33.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.52,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:39.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:42.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something I wrote a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:45.09,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Imatake kept bugging me to show it to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:47.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,so I just happened to bring it with me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:51.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it compares with Imatake's series, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:56.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, seeing as you used to worked with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:59.21,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the editors will all be delighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.27,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:03.44,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's only the prologue to an especially long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:04.81,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We would be very grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:07.81,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,if you would continue to write for {\i1}Literature Era{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:11.45,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, I'm busy enough as it is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.45,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can't I persuade you somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:16.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very well! I shall write for the late Imatake's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:22.40,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! I have to be going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:24.16,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:25.46,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You heard that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:30.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem I must hurry back home and get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:34.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For Imatake, who was killed by some idiot who just wanted his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:38.21,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's no question about it—he's the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:40.41,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But he has an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:45.04,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How? How was he able to take that picture?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:51.92,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's more, the camera was untampered, and he had Ran use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:55.59,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A picture at 8:50 wouldn't serve as an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:00.13,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Darn it! There has to be something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:02.80,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Something that will bring his alibi crumbling down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:05.79,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Think back to when you met him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:09.38,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Sorry, but I need to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:10.54,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:12.53,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.78,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Sure is hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.85,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He didn't take his jacket off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.42,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Or maybe he couldn't take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:20.82,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.92,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Could you take a picture for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.66,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Here's the camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:27.32,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Could you take it with that "Ichi" character behind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:34.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I still want to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:37.70,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You just never give up!\NKeep harassing me and I'll sue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:42.07,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Aha, so that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:44.31,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now I've got this trick figured out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:46.45,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Just as I thought, he is the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:49.97,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's more, this was a premeditated murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:04.87,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I've got the trick behind his alibi photo completely figured out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.48,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I better let the detective know before it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.48,0:15:10.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:12.82,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:15.19,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:17.85,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}OK! Time for my secret weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:36.21,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now to set his pose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:38.20,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...arrange the photographs on the desk...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:45.21,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...and then use this Voice-Altering Bow Tie to mimic his voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:53.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.53,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:58.27,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have photographic proof it wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:04.41,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Detective. Could you tell him how incompetent he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:06.88,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Incompetent he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:10.51,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You really disappoint me, Detective Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:12.35,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:17.92,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I kept quiet so you could have all of the credit,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:23.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,yet you were still fooled by the trick\Nused to make that alibi photograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:24.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So then he is—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:25.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:29.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The one who killed Mr. Satoru Imatake is none other than...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:32.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the one standing next to you—Norikazu Sasai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.74,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:40.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you the one who said this was a robbery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:47.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I said that so you would lower your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:49.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I knew from the very instant I saw the victim
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:52.88,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,that the murderer was an acquaintance of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.26,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Based on what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:59.66,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The toothpaste foam in the victim's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:02.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His toothbrush was also lying on the ground near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:05.27,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the victim was brushing his teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.70,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,before he was shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:12.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So? Everyone brushes their teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.21,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:19.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not very common for people to open the front door for strangers
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:24.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,while still brushing their teeth, now is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:31.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing—this room's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:35.96,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer fled immediately after the gunshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:40.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it would be possible to ransack this entire room
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,in such a short amount of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:48.74,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely it was done purposely before the murder
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:52.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,to make it look like an ordinary robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:55.52,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:18:00.26,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All of the evidence at the scene of the crime seems to point to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:03.36,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I have an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:07.09,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How do you explain that photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:11.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is most likely a picture that you took
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:14.87,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,when you came to a previous festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:18.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You then held on to the camera until today's festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:24.78,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,where you ran into Ran and had her continue taking more pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:27.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Although it was an extremely simple trick,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:29.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,the fact that you were wearing the exact same clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:32.99,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,made it easy to mistake it\Nfor a picture you took today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:34.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:37.63,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The reason you endured the heat\Nand kept your jacket on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:42.70,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,was because you didn't want to look any different than in the 1st photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:44.36,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:50.67,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a splendid sense of imagination, Detective Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:57.11,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But do you have any proof that I took\Nthat picture at a previous festival?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:19:00.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why, yes, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.51,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:09.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's right here in this picture! Your-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:11.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:14.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be bothering Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:21.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:22.43,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:30.51,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I leave the rest to you, Detective Yokomizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:31.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.31,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His wrist?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:44.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, I forgot my watch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:58.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:03.01,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How do you explain this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:08.92,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your wrist is perfectly{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} tan{\r} in your alibi photograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:11.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yet your wrist is white now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:16.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is that you took this picture one year ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:20.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Sasai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:24.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I concede defeat, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:31.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to get rid of Imatake one year ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:34.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to take his place at the top of the literary world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:40.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. One year ago, it was decided that my work
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:43.02,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,would be published as a series in {\i1}Literature Era{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:48.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But right before the deadline,\Nthe editors switched to Imatake instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:53.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Simply because he had a better reputation than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:21:00.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that series as my last\Nchance to make it as a writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:02.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But then he had to go and snatch it away,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:04.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,almost as if he was ridiculing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:07.51,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So then you killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:10.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:16.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:20.69,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,About Imatake's work that won the Naomoto Award...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:24.19,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We both thought up the story for it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.19,0:21:28.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,back when Imatake and I used to write together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:32.66,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Though I suppose nobody would believe me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:19.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent detective work, Detective Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.32,0:23:22.46,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was all thanks to you\Nthat we were able to solve the case
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:25.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and arrest Sasai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:28.07,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Case? Arrest? Sasai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:29.83,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop pretending!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.83,0:23:31.07,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:33.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I always knew Sasai was the killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:34.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I just wasted time to make filler!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:36.57,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:51.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keep laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:02.78,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you going in?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.78,0:24:04.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have business in there, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.69,0:24:10.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You went out with Shin'ichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.96,0:24:14.63,Dialogue,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The lock has marks on it from being tampered with...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.63,0:24:16.30,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a kidnapping, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.30,0:24:19.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally found you, Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.50,0:24:21.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi! Come out this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:24.41,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.00,0:24:29.92,Dialogue Top,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.92,0:24:34.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Video Game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.08,0:24:38.60,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Even next time, there is always one truth!
